{"tid":2415030,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Citadel對沖基金創始人：仍對加密貨幣表示不屑一顧，稱看不到其“經濟基礎”","createTime":"2021-02-20T02:18:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T02:33:40.000Z","uid":63934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6148d81b586fe209f02c93def3f6f18203edc3b9","tid":2415030,"uid":63934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T02:18:17.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"https://m.hk.investing.com/news/stock-market-news/article-139147[/url］\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hk.investing.com%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-news%2Farticle-139147%5B%2Furl%EF%BC%BD&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2Bbkt5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=4d737d45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.hk.investing.com/news/stock-market-news/article-139147[/url］</a><br />\n<br />\n智通財經APP獲悉，周五，比特幣在美股盤中突破54000美元/枚，創下曆史新高，盡管一部分投資者將這種新興資産視爲金融的未來，Citadel對沖基金創始人Ken Griffin仍對加密貨幣表示不屑一顧。<br />\nGriffin稱：&ldquo;我只是沒有花太多時間在思考加密貨幣&hellip;&hellip;我看不到加密貨幣的經濟基礎。我了解如何估價股票、如何考慮全球貨幣彙率，我不知道如何考慮什麽是有效的數字代幣。&rdquo;<br />\n比特幣在最近幾個月飛漲，部分原因是該數字貨幣得到了主流金融機構、投資者和知名企業的接納和認可。美國最古老的銀行紐約梅隆銀行本月初表示，將開始推出比特幣和其他數字貨幣的相關服務受比特幣上漲推助，美股區塊鏈板塊暴漲，截至周五收盤，人人網(<a href=\"http://REN.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FREN.US&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2Bbkt5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=c6bfa802\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">REN.US</a>)漲超36%，嘉楠科技(<a href=\"http://CAN.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FCAN.US&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2Bbkt5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=fd535d91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">CAN.US</a>)漲超43%，迅雷(<a href=\"http://XNET.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FXNET.US&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2Bbkt5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=f4263d68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">XNET.US</a>)漲超22%，第九城市(<a href=\"http://NCTY.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FNCTY.US&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2Bbkt5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=6c05a5d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">NCTY.US</a>)漲超31%，Riot Blockchain(<a href=\"http://RIOT.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FRIOT.US&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2Bbkt5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=c2a37783\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">RIOT.US</a>)漲超14%。<br />\nCitadel Securities是做市商，處理了美國約40%的日常零售交易，是涉及美國金融管道的最大公司之一。Griffin還創立了一家名爲Citadel的對沖基金。在稍早發生的遊戲驿站(<a href=\"http://GME.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGME.US&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2Bbkt5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=d9215a7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">GME.US</a>)軋空事件中，Citadel對沖基金向遊戲驿站做空方損失最大的Melvin Capital進行了注資。"},{"pid":"ca25f5ee086aa113ac6563bc09745229ed13ab6f","tid":2415030,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T02:23:57.000Z","msg":"繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連你都認同就要走鬼"},{"pid":"934a2d037384fd77855dbd80c77e4025b6e7f863","tid":2415030,"uid":271353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T02:26:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd92e39d25d9a9c58116b4983808ff125f0654a","tid":2415030,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T02:27:29.000Z","msg":"it's a scam<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d737a3c91ea0a8812652f5fa7ae5ab60c4d7c7","tid":2415030,"uid":82033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T02:28:58.000Z","msg":"可以沽空 Citadel 了"},{"pid":"1dea482fc8e4ab1755c04f3ae4a80e6709acbbde","tid":2415030,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T02:33:40.000Z","msg":"其實佢講得幾好，不過市埸係唔理性，八成人都想一夜暴富"}]}